name: Power Button Collector (Mini Jam 73)
description:
This is my Entry for Mini Jam 73. The theme was/is power so I made a game where you have to collect power buttons.  To move you use the A and D or arrow keys. To jump you use the space bar. 

Any and all feedback is welcome . 

Good Luck and Have Fun!

Art and Code by:  Liam_x220
